    "description": "Are you a skilled Logistics Manager looking for your next big career move? Nimbus Post Holdings Services in Vijayawada offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Nimbus Post Holdings Services:\nNimbus Post Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nimbus Post Holdings Services!",
